  <name>Ashen Surge</name>
  <description><![CDATA[You step into Ashen Surge with a long ember of steady heat, then the storm arrives: 5x45s lightning bolts and 5x30s razor sparks. Each lull is a breath through soot before the next flare crawls up the spine.]]></description>
  <sportType>bike</sportType>
  <tags>
  </tags>
